show.description: Wrongfully accused and betrayed by her demon-cultivator sister, Grace Braylon dies — only to be reborn through excruciating pain. She leaves her sect and emotions behind to walk the ruthless Path of Merciless cultivation. With vengeance in her heart, every step forward is a battle against the past.
